Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛翔 - 犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.62,0:23:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那裡嗎？
